# Environment Variables
# The following variables can be configured for ScrcpyGUI Pro build & dev:

# Uncomment to run debug locally with a specific VITE port (default 1420)
# PORT=1420
# VITE_PORT=1420

# If you use custom API services, define them here. Note: Secret keys WITHOUT the VITE_ prefix
# will NOT be exposed to the bundled frontend code!

# VITE_API_ENDPOINT=https://your-custom-analytics.com/api
# SECRET_KEY=123-your-secret-key-123
